7ii.)If Django didn't know which settings module to load, what kinds of failures would you expect when starting the application?

    Django won't start because it doesn't know where the settings configuration is.
    To make it even more precise:
    Without the settings module, Django doesn't know things like:
        - Which apps are installed
        - Which database to connect to
        - Which middleware to use
        - Which authentication backend to load
        - Where static and media files live

    So Django fails very early in its startup process.

